{"article_id":"0ENoigDbYbNkJhuw","edus":[{"id":0,"text":"Congressman Devin Nunes briefs reporters on Capitol Hill , March 24 , 2017 .","depth":2},{"id":1,"text":"( Jonathan Ernst/Reuters )","depth":2},{"id":2,"text":"The Nunes memo has been released","depth":5},{"id":3,"text":"and America ' s national security has not ,","depth":6},{"id":4,"text":"as far as we can tell ,","depth":7},{"id":5,"text":"been irreparably harmed .","depth":7},{"id":6,"text":"The campaign","depth":7},{"id":7,"text":"waged against the memo as a grave threat to America ' s intelligence operations","depth":7},{"id":8,"text":"appears completely absurd in light of its contents .","depth":6},{"id":9,"text":"Part of the bureaucratic objection at the FBI to releasing the memo","depth":7},{"id":10,"text":"- and to giving the House Intelligence Committee the material","depth":8},{"id":11,"text":"it ' s based on -","depth":8},{"id":12,"text":"was clearly that it contained information embarrassing to the FBI .","depth":6},{"id":13,"text":"The memo was always going to labor under unrealistic expectations .","depth":5},{"id":14,"text":"It couldn ' t possibly live up to its advance billing from Sean Hannity and Co.","depth":7},{"id":15,"text":"that it was Watergate and the Lindbergh-baby kidnapping all wrapped into one .","depth":7},{"id":16,"text":"But it adds to our understanding of the beginnings of the Russia investigation","depth":7},{"id":17,"text":"and raises questions about its provenance .","depth":7},{"id":18,"text":"According to the memo ,","depth":9},{"id":19,"text":"FBI deputy director Andrew McCabe told the committee","depth":10},{"id":20,"text":"that there would have been no Foreign Intelligence Surveillance Act","depth":15},{"id":21,"text":"( FISA )","depth":15},{"id":22,"text":"application to surveil former Trump-campaign adviser Carter Page","depth":14},{"id":23,"text":"absent the information in the so-called Steele dossier .","depth":13},{"id":24,"text":"That ' s the lurid oppo document","depth":13},{"id":25,"text":"produced by former British spy Christopher Steele ,","depth":14},{"id":26,"text":"who worked for the research firm Fusion GPS","depth":15},{"id":27,"text":"that the Democrats paid","depth":16},{"id":28,"text":"to dig up dirt on Trump .","depth":16},{"id":29,"text":"The memo says","depth":12},{"id":30,"text":"that the partisan source of the document wasn ' t made clear to the FISA court ;","depth":13},{"id":31,"text":"that the dossier was largely unverified ;","depth":14},{"id":32,"text":"and that Steele made his anti-Trump agenda clear to the FBI .","depth":14},{"id":33,"text":"This suggests sloppiness on the part of the FBI , and perhaps something worse .","depth":9},{"id":34,"text":"Certainly ,","depth":10},{"id":35,"text":"if this were a Democratic president","depth":12},{"id":36,"text":"who was the subject of an investigation","depth":13},{"id":37,"text":"that began , in part , on the basis of partisan information ,","depth":13},{"id":38,"text":"Democrats would be running around with their hair on fire","depth":12},{"id":39,"text":"( and the press wouldn ' t be outraged by congressional oversight","depth":13},{"id":40,"text":"to get to the bottom of the matter ) .","depth":13},{"id":41,"text":"One argument","depth":10},{"id":42,"text":"made against the memo","depth":10},{"id":43,"text":"is that it is \" partisan. \"","depth":9},{"id":44,"text":"Well , yes ,","depth":11},{"id":45,"text":"and so is everything","depth":12},{"id":46,"text":"that Adam Schiff does .","depth":12},{"id":47,"text":"Yet Schiff doesn ' t appear to have any trouble getting reporters on the phone .","depth":10},{"id":48,"text":"A high-stakes Washington investigation such as this will always become politicized ,","depth":10},{"id":49,"text":"with the two parties clashing over what ' s most important and how to interpret facts .","depth":10},{"id":50,"text":"Another argument is that the FISA surveillance was of Carter Page , the eccentric low-level Trump-campaign foreign-policy aide","depth":11},{"id":51,"text":"who has obnoxiously pro-Kremlin views .","depth":11},{"id":52,"text":"So , why should anyone be concerned ?","depth":10},{"id":53,"text":"He was already ,","depth":11},{"id":54,"text":"it is said ,","depth":11},{"id":55,"text":"on the FBI radar screen .","depth":10},{"id":56,"text":"Page isn ' t our cup of tea ,","depth":10},{"id":57,"text":"but","depth":11},{"id":58,"text":"when he first came to the attention of the FBI years ago ,","depth":12},{"id":59,"text":"he cooperated with the bureau in an investigation of a Russian spy .","depth":12},{"id":60,"text":"The widespread presumption","depth":11},{"id":61,"text":"that he is dirty","depth":11},{"id":62,"text":"hasn ' t been proven .","depth":10},{"id":63,"text":"Yet another is that the memo acknowledges","depth":10},{"id":64,"text":"that the Russian investigation didn ' t begin with Page ,","depth":11},{"id":65,"text":"but with George Papadopoulos months earlier and with no connection to the dossier .","depth":11},{"id":66,"text":"But there is no indication","depth":10},{"id":67,"text":"that this was anything other than a ministerial act ,","depth":12},{"id":68,"text":"i.e. , a formal opening of a case","depth":12},{"id":69,"text":"with no action","depth":12},{"id":70,"text":"taken","depth":13},{"id":71,"text":"to follow up .","depth":13},{"id":72,"text":"So the Carter Page surveillance may well have been the main event .","depth":8},{"id":73,"text":"Finally , the FBI says","depth":8},{"id":74,"text":"that the memo has material omissions ,","depth":8},{"id":75,"text":"and Democrats contest key allegations in it .","depth":7},{"id":76,"text":"Resolving this shouldn ' t be difficult :","depth":7},{"id":77,"text":"The counter-memo","depth":9},{"id":78,"text":"produced by the Democrats","depth":9},{"id":79,"text":"should be released , as well as underlying material","depth":9},{"id":80,"text":"including the transcript of the interview with Andrew McCabe ,","depth":10},{"id":81,"text":"which has become the subject of a he-said/he-said between committee Republicans and Democrats .","depth":10},{"id":82,"text":"Perhaps the surveillance of Page bore some fruit ;","depth":7},{"id":83,"text":"if so ,","depth":8},{"id":84,"text":"we should hear about it .","depth":8},{"id":85,"text":"The more information the public can get about all of this , the better .","depth":6},{"id":86,"text":"There is speculation that President Trump might , in response to the memo ,","depth":9},{"id":87,"text":"fire Deputy Attorney General Rod Rosenstein ,","depth":10},{"id":88,"text":"who oversaw one of the renewals of FISA warrants on Carter Page .","depth":10},{"id":89,"text":"Trump made one of his patented ambiguously threatening remarks about this possibility on Friday .","depth":8},{"id":90,"text":"If he were to move against Rosenstein ,","depth":8},{"id":91,"text":"it might cause a semi-collapse of his Justice Department ,","depth":9},{"id":92,"text":"give further fodder to Robert Mueller ,","depth":10},{"id":93,"text":"and undo the political headway","depth":11},{"id":94,"text":"Republicans have made in recent weeks .","depth":11},{"id":95,"text":"Trump should sit tight","depth":7},{"id":96,"text":"and","depth":8},{"id":97,"text":"- if the investigation is as unfounded","depth":10},{"id":98,"text":"as he says -","depth":10},{"id":99,"text":"await his eventual vindication .","depth":9},{"id":100,"text":"The more information the public can get about all of this , the better .","depth":5},{"id":101,"text":"The Nunes memo has broken the seal on information","depth":7},{"id":102,"text":"related to the start of the Russian investigation ;","depth":7},{"id":103,"text":"the republic will survive ,","depth":7},{"id":104,"text":"and in fact , benefit from an airing of the circumstances of this episode .","depth":7},{"id":105,"text":"Memo Details","depth":5},{"id":106,"text":"Use of Dossier","depth":6},{"id":107,"text":"to Spy on Trump Adviser","depth":6},{"id":108,"text":"Contrary to Democrat Claims ,","depth":5},{"id":109,"text":"Nunes Memo Doesn ' t Threaten National Security","depth":5}],"relations":[{"parent":219,"left":111,"right":218,"relation":"context","nuclearity":"SN"},{"parent":111,"left":0,"right":1,"relation":"attribution","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":218,"left":190,"right":217,"relation":"joint","nuclearity":"NN"},{"parent":190,"left":121,"right":189,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":121,"left":114,"right":120,"relation":"evaluation","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":114,"left":2,"right":113,"relation":"causal","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":113,"left":3,"right":112,"relation":"same-unit","nuclearity":"NN"},{"parent":112,"left":4,"right":5,"relation":"evaluation","nuclearity":"SN"},{"parent":120,"left":116,"right":119,"relation":"explanation","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":116,"left":115,"right":8,"relation":"same-unit","nuclearity":"NN"},{"parent":115,"left":6,"right":7,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":119,"left":118,"right":12,"relation":"same-unit","nuclearity":"NN"},{"parent":118,"left":9,"right":117,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":117,"left":10,"right":11,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":189,"left":125,"right":188,"relation":"explanation","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":125,"left":13,"right":124,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":124,"left":122,"right":123,"relation":"adversative","nuclearity":"SN"},{"parent":122,"left":14,"right":15,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":123,"left":16,"right":17,"relation":"joint","nuclearity":"NN"},{"parent":188,"left":179,"right":187,"relation":"joint","nuclearity":"NN"},{"parent":179,"left":156,"right":178,"relation":"joint","nuclearity":"NN"},{"parent":156,"left":147,"right":155,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":147,"left":139,"right":146,"relation":"evaluation","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":139,"left":18,"right":138,"relation":"attribution","n